      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "[9/1558] al-Kafi: Ali b. Ibrahim from his father from Ibn Abi Umayr from Muawiya b. Ammar from Abi Abdillah عليه السلام who said: If al-Ḥamd were recited upon a dead body seventy times and the soul is returned into it (i.e. the dead body) that would not be surprising"
